com.viewlift.views.customviews

Class ViewCreator.OnSeasonSelectedListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.viewlift.views.customviews.ViewCreator.OnSeasonSelectedListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.widget.AdapterView.OnItemSelectedListener, OnInternalEvent
    Enclosing class:
    ViewCreator

    private static class ViewCreator.OnSeasonSelectedListener
extends java.lang.Object
implements android.widget.AdapterView.OnItemSelectedListener, OnInternalEvent
    This class is used to handle events when a season is selected from the dropdown box. It will send an event message to repopulate the view with a list of episodes from the given season.
